Method Detail

addMappable

public boolean addMappable(Mappable m)
Adds a Mappable Object to the Map.

Adds a Mappable to an empty tile on the map and then marks that tile as MAPPABLE. If there already is a Mappable in the position, it is still added and all current Mappables at that tile will be put into an ArrayList.

Parameters:
m - The Mappable that needs to be added.
Returns:
true if the add was successful, false otherwise.
